{"tid":2366504,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天津一間公司發生燃氣爆炸　造成1死7傷","createTime":"2021-01-14T14:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T14:23:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"44ba988e643f64c98d1fad4a8d8537ba25c3051b","tid":2366504,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T14:07:50.000Z","msg":"天津一間公司發生燃氣爆炸事故，造成1人死亡，7人受傷，事故原因正在調查。<br />\n<br />\n事發在下午1時前，位於天津空港經濟區的一間汽車零部件公司，一個廠房發生燃氣爆炸，事發後當地應急管理局及消防趕到現場處理，搜救行動已經結束，無人被困。"},{"pid":"9381906340aa7fa1484445b10a8a49e85f9581dd","tid":2366504,"uid":178187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T14:08:47.000Z","msg":"10人死亡，70人受傷"},{"pid":"8ed92b5cda3da70f664c29047d10f0d99abdba28","tid":2366504,"uid":141664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T14:10:16.000Z","msg":"取暖姐，小事啦"},{"pid":"10685e4eb340333448ef8f3cad192e4c096734eb","tid":2366504,"uid":245484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T14:23:58.000Z","msg":"氣炸師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}